body:

We are happy to provide you with information that will help you to check-in for the coference.

###  Getting to the Venue
The Darmstadtium lies in the heart of Darmstadt and is [easy to navigate to](https://www.darmstadtium.de/kontakt/anreise-2).

### Early Check-In on Tuesday 
* 15:00 - 18:00 at Darmstadtium

Most participants will arrive on Wednesday morning. 
To reduce queuing on Wednesday, we offer early badge collection on Tuesday. 
If you are already in the town, we recommend that you take advantage of the early check-in. It will significantly improve your check-in experience.


### The registration desk 
The registration desk is at the Darmstadtium. 
It is open in the hours:
* Tuesday 15:00 - 18:00 
* Wednesday 08:30 - 17:00 
* Thursday 08:30 - 17:00 
* Friday 08:30 - 17:00 

### Badge pick-up

* Proceed to the registration desk.
* Badges are ordered alphabetically by the FIRST name. Please check the signs where to que up.
* There is only one collection point for all badges. There are only a separate collection points for sponsors. 
* Please present your ID to pick up your badge, students please present your student ID.

### T-shirt pick-up

If you have pre-ordered a T-Shirt with your ticket, please pick-up it nearby the registration desk.


### Luggages and Jackets

There is a cloakroam at Level 1 of the Darmstadtium easily accomodating your coat. We can store suitcases in the garderobe if leaving at hotel is not an option.

### Seats in the tutorial rooms are limited. 

Please follow our blog post on how to reserve your spot.